      "factId": "hz.web.449627d44882ccf7.fact.1",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "The Syntax of Credit Card Numbers The Syntax of Credit Card Numbers Steven Pemberton , CWI , Amsterdam Abstract The numbers on credit cards (and other similar identification numbers) consist of a string of digits.",
      "tokens": [
        "syntax",
        "credit",
        "card",
        "numbers",
