      ]
    },
    {
      "charEnd": 650,
      "charStart": 369,
      "factId": "hz.web.449627d44882ccf7.fact.2",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "These are traditionally checked for semi-validity using the Luhn algorithm, defined in Annex B of ISO/IEC 7812-1, which is a right-to-left mathematical check-sum style algorithm that guards against common errors such as mistyping single digits, and interchanging adjacent digits.",
      "tokens": [
